OL,3,CTeen accused of attacking teacher
OL,4,Cbrought knife to school to 'show off'
OL,6,FA teenage boy accused of attacking a
OL,7,Fteacher at Milford Haven Comprehensive
OL,8,Fschool in February this year says he
OL,9,Fbrought a large kitchen knife into
OL,10,Fschool "to show off" to his friends.
OL,12,FSpeaking for the first time during the
OL,13,Ftrial on Monday 13 July, the
OL,14,Fdefendant, who cannot be named for
OL,15,Flegal reasons, denied using the knife
OL,16,Fto deliberately cause harm to his
OL,17,Fteacher.
OL,26,@rD@HOUrD@TO]
