OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1784035119
OL,3,CTeen accused of attacking teacher
OL,4,Cbrought knife to school to 'show off'
OL,6,FTaking questions from Matthew Roberts
OL,7,FKC for the defence, the teenager spoke
OL,8,Fabout teacher Mrs Vicki Williams,
OL,9,Fsaying "she was nice".
OL,11,FMr Roberts asked: "Had you ever had
OL,12,Fany bad arguments or fallings out with
OL,13,Fher?"
OL,15,FThe defendant replied: "No."
OL,26,@qD@HOUsD@SOUuD@EO]wD@XOUwD@\O]
