PN,43703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1784035119
OL,3,CTeen accused of attacking teacher
OL,4,Cbrought knife to school to 'show off'
OL,6,FWhen quizzed on the reason he had
OL,7,Fbrought the largest kitchen knife from
OL,8,Fhis family home onto the school
OL,9,Fgrounds, the defendant said he "wanted
OL,10,Fto impress and show off to (his)
OL,11,Ffriends".
OL,13,FHe later added that his friend group
OL,14,Fwould bring in random tools and
OL,15,Fhousehold items.
OL,17,F"We did this for a while. To see what
OL,18,Fwe could get away with in school," he
OL,19,Fsaid.JThe boy denied wanting to use
OL,20,Fthe knife on anybody in a violent
OL,21,Fmanner.
OL,26,@qD@`OUrD@\pmrD@`pnsD@HO]yD@AOUzD@bO]
