PN,43704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1784035119
OL,3,CTeen accused of attacking teacher
OL,4,Cbrought knife to school to 'show off'
OL,6,FWhen asked if he saw the knife making
OL,7,Fcontact with Ms Williams' head, the
OL,8,Fteenager replied "no", but added he
OL,9,Faccepted that it must have.
OL,11,FHe was also asked about how he felt
OL,12,Fafter being arrested. To which he
OL,13,Freplied: "Nothing really. I was still
OL,14,Fin shock."
OL,16,FThe 16-year-old defendant previously
OL,17,Fpleaded not guilty to the three
OL,18,Fcharges he faces - attempted murder,
OL,19,Funlawful wounding, and wounding with
OL,20,Fintent to cause grievous bodily harm.
